* Grandchildren - Shomita Karmakar, Rinky Karmakar, Siddharth Karmakar, Shubhankar Banerjee, Priyanka Choudhuri, Gaurang Karmakar, Anuradha Karmakar, Sean Karmakar, Steve Karmakar

